text.section:
In accordance with § 4-742 of this title, the Department of the Environment may close to the catching, planting, or harvesting of shellfish waters in:
The shellfish public fishery area;
An Aquaculture Enterprise Zone;
An area preapproved for leasing in the Atlantic Coastal Bays; or
An area subject to an aquaculture lease, submerged land lease, or demonstration lease.
